  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Half board meals are served in the hotel's restaurant which looks out onto the gardens and the lake. Breakfast is a buffet and for dinner you'll have a four-course evening meal that includes a delicious cheese course, during the high season there is a choice of main course. When the weather's nice you can even have your dinner on the terrace.</p>
<p>Early meals for children are available on request.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
